de.braintags.io.vertx.pojomapper.typehandler

Interface ITypeHandlerReferenced

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, ITypeHandler

    public interface ITypeHandlerReferenced
extends ITypeHandler
    A special interface for alle ITypeHandler which are dealing with fields, annotated as Referenced. Those ITypeHandler are storing an instance of IObjectReference in the first run, and in the second run those references are resolved for the real objects to avoid hirarchical conflicts
